Band Biography[]

Forming in the midst of the ever-volatile Seattle scene from the ashes of a variety of legendary punk and hardcore bands, Pretty Girls Make Graves released their first EP in 2001 and have since followed it up with three albums showcasing a remarkable degree of maturity in pace, presentation and technical prowess.
